name: Celeste
description:
Celeste is a general-purpose stable diffusion illustrations model. This is an overhaul / modernization of the Celeste - Legacy model.

The example images have been generated using CelesteV2 with a HIRES fix immediately applied to them during generation.

Make sure to use at least a value of 50 or more steps + a HIRES fix for the best results!

Goes without question, you can use this model and any generated images without crediting me or the model though I would greatly appreciate if you could show me your generations <3
